 *         Vcc  Vcc       Vcc = 3.3 V
 *          |    |         |
 *         4K7  4K7       1k0  pull up resistors (3K3 to 10K Ohm)
 *          |    |   +-|<|-+   LED red (led not possible when pir is installed)
 *          |    |                                           +--------+
